      • startPathSearch

        public void startPathSearch(MapPoint startPoint,
                            java.util.List<MapPoint> targets,
                            PathSearchMode mode)
        Starts search of new route between given points. The mode changes the behavior of the algorithm. Searching in fast mode finds the fastest path. The optimal mode avoids places that are difficult to access but does not exclude more difficult routes. Comfort mode more strongly avoids hard-to-reach locations than the optimal mode.
        Parameters:
        startPoint - start point
        targets - list of possible targets
        mode - mode of algorithm behavior
